<a name="The-Definition-of-append_002dto_002dbuffer"></a>
<h3 class="section">4.4 The Definition of <code>append-to-buffer</code></h3>
<a name="index-append_002dto_002dbuffer"></a>

<p>The <code>append-to-buffer</code> command is more complex than the
<code>mark-whole-buffer</code> command.  What it does is copy the region
(that is, the part of the buffer between point and mark) from the
current buffer to a specified buffer.
</p>
