</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top">&bull; <a href="#if-_0026-or" accesskey="4">if &amp; or</a>:</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">Using an <code>if</code> instead of an <code>or</code>.
</td></tr>
