<a name="Build-a-list"></a>
<div class="header">
<p>
Next: <a href="#length" accesskey="n" rel="next">length</a>, Up: <a href="#cons" accesskey="u" rel="up">cons</a> &nbsp; [<a href="#SEC_Contents" title="Table of contents" rel="contents">Contents</a>][<a href="#Index" title="Index" rel="index">Index</a>]</p>
