<a name="zap_002dto_002dchar-1"></a>
<h3 class="section">8.1 <code>zap-to-char</code></h3>
<a name="index-zap_002dto_002dchar"></a>

<p>Let us look at the interactive <code>zap-to-char</code> function.
</p>
