<a name="Lisp-macro"></a>
<div class="header">
<p>
Previous: <a href="#condition_002dcase" accesskey="p" rel="prev">condition-case</a>, Up: <a href="#kill_002dregion" accesskey="u" rel="up">kill-region</a> &nbsp; [<a href="#SEC_Contents" title="Table of contents" rel="contents">Contents</a>][<a href="#Index" title="Index" rel="index">Index</a>]</p>
