</td></tr>
<tr><td align="left" valign="top">&bull; <a href="#copy_002dregion_002das_002dkill-body" accesskey="2">copy-region-as-kill body</a>:</td><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align="left" valign="top">The body of <code>copy-region-as-kill</code>.
