<div class="header">
<p>
Next: <a href="#search-Exercises" accesskey="n" rel="next">search Exercises</a>, Previous: <a href="#defvar" accesskey="p" rel="prev">defvar</a>, Up: <a href="#Cutting-_0026-Storing-Text" accesskey="u" rel="up">Cutting &amp; Storing Text</a> &nbsp; [<a href="#SEC_Contents" title="Table of contents" rel="contents">Contents</a>][<a href="#Index" title="Index" rel="index">Index</a>]</p>
