<a name="Complete-forward_002dsentence"></a>
<div class="header">
<p>
Next: <a href="#fwd_002dsentence-while-loops" accesskey="n" rel="next">fwd-sentence while loops</a>, Up: <a href="#forward_002dsentence" accesskey="u" rel="up">forward-sentence</a> &nbsp; [<a href="#SEC_Contents" title="Table of contents" rel="contents">Contents</a>][<a href="#Index" title="Index" rel="index">Index</a>]</p>
