<h2 class="appendix">Appendix B Handling the Kill Ring</h2>
<a name="index-Kill-ring-handling"></a>
<a name="index-Handling-the-kill-ring"></a>
<a name="index-Ring_002c-making-a-list-like-a"></a>

<p>The kill ring is a list that is transformed into a ring by the
workings of the <code>current-kill</code> function.  The <code>yank</code> and
<code>yank-pop</code> commands use the <code>current-kill</code> function.
</p>
<p>This appendix describes the <code>current-kill</code> function as well as
both the <code>yank</code> and the <code>yank-pop</code> commands, but first,
consider the workings of the kill ring.
</p>
